libcompizconfig: libcompiz-config (Compiz-Fusion Settings Library)
libcompizconfig:
libcompizconfig: Compiz-Fusion is a compositing window manager that uses 3D graphics 
libcompizconfig: acceleration via OpenGL. It provides various new graphical effects 
libcompizconfig: and features on any desktop environment, including GNOME. It is the 
libcompizconfig: result of the re-unification of the Beryl-project and the community 
libcompizconfig: around the Compiz Window Manager. 
libcompizconfig: 
libcompizconfig: This package provides development files for the compiz-fusion 
libcompizconfig: configuration system.
